description: This file declares APIs for the PowerManagement object, including functions to get, set, validate, commit, and rollback parameters related to power management. It primarily contains function prototypes and include guards, serving as an interface for power management features in the software project.

methods.name: PowerManagement_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean parameter value related to power management.

methods.name: PowerManagement_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets a boolean parameter value related to power management.

methods.name: PowerManagement_Validate
methods.description: Validates the current power management parameters before applying changes.

methods.name: PowerManagement_Commit
methods.description: Commits the current power management parameters to make them effective.

methods.name: PowerManagement_Rollback
methods.description: Reverts changes made to power management parameters.
